content: I've been tracking my body fat percentage and skeletal muscle percentage, and I'm happy to see that I've made some progress over the past month. Speaking of progress, I also got my blood pressure monitor calibrated at the doctor's office last week, and it's been showing more accurate readings since then. I've been using it to track my blood pressure regularly, especially since my doctor told me that I need to keep an eye on it due to my family history.
